overview: The film of the unique physical challenge. Legendary athlete Joss Naylor wanted to commemorate 50 years of competitive fell running.  On the longest day of the year he set off from Mungriside in the northern fells to run home to Greens Dale in the Wasdale valley.
tagline: Joss Naylor 35 miles,  20 Lake Land peaks, 18000 feet of ascent in under 15 hours and all at the age of 73
title: Joss Naylor - Iron Man
